{"tid":303482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"明明分左手了","createTime":"2017-06-30T08:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T20:05:43.000Z","uid":81012,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccb866a4bec08afb19c3aa42ad4b952591e8deb","tid":303482,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"將自己個contact name set左以前set佢既名<br />\n令到自己可以wtsapp自己<br />\n打曬想對佢講既說話<br />\n雖然唔會有回應<br />\n<br />\n岩岩見到有人係group tag自己<br />\n見到佢個名個心緊張左一下 以為佢搵我<br />\n點知係自己多心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\non9仔"},{"pid":"46e4a338e6815cdcc5f39555251ccae2f9fd0af1","tid":303482,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過"},{"pid":"7cda50f80edfa7e2c0c7ef94035ad3d91be4aff4","tid":303482,"uid":32022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab65406e3bfe4bebd46925c65e2a3111d1e5b2b","tid":303482,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然佢都同我講時間會沖淡一切<br />\n但我唔想完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無力感好辛苦<br />\n當佢已經對呢段關係死心<br />\n做咩都無用<br />\n唯一可以做既就係放佢走<br />\n雖然好想繼續相愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但知足的快樂叫我忍受心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4daac6b654f8fa3e0cbbdfe485aa134776ddfa0","tid":303482,"uid":81012,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇住一個曾經相愛既人<br />\n係幾日內由情人變陌生人<br />\n個心唔知點解就好酸好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594531503b2eba33a87af41baa6b3e6b1f4e4311","tid":303482,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2a84005d89981ce971f5abd51db4cfb56532be","tid":303482,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然佢都同我講時間會沖淡一切<br />\n但我唔想完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無力感好辛苦<br />\n當佢已經對呢段關係死心<br />\n做咩都無用<br />\n唯一可以做既就係放佢走<br />\n雖然好想繼續相愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但知足的快樂叫我