\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵人吹下水囉,講出嚟會好過d<br />\n有d感受收收埋埋反而仲難受</blockquote><br />\n呢幾日已經有同人傾過 喊過<br />\n可能果刻會好d<br />\n但轉個頭又好心痛<br />\n做咩都無心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老土都咁話啦,要時間去接受嘅<br />\n未必個個得,但除咗咁,仲可以點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人同我講過,當你唔開心,覺得咩都無心機做係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過,如果你想慢慢好返,咪照返之前嘅軌跡生活,該返學嘅時候返學,該食嘅時候食,該返工就返工<br />\n你會發現你做嘅嘢同你嘅情緒係雙向,慢慢,會適應返...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8249af81907d4b83aeccf33e8ffe65f1a9a30d","tid":303482,"uid":112950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"唉...我都失戀。自己一個係街度喊，仲比人話我嗮佢時間..重點我同佢分完手之後自己又要掛住人，又想揾翻人，又唔捨得人。喊到成隻狗咁，有冇人可以屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24cb33a41587b555bb7fa48e36aa95992925942","tid":303482,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉...我都失戀。自己一個係街度喊，仲比人話我嗮佢時間..重點我同佢分完手之後自己又要掛住人，又想揾翻人，又唔捨得人。喊到成隻狗咁，有冇人可以屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人老狗就堅強d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c01bfe88eceaa1481e6c52e320f3831a35f64b3","tid":303482,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"點解分手"},{"pid":"eb3f0c059f6c5fee10dcc34b30c53c39939b9f4b","tid":303482,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女朋友分手之後用一個月就變左人地女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye